2 关键配置","value":"42-关键配置","line":56,"column":0,"depth":3},"43-开始烧录":{"type":"header","text":"4.3 开始烧录","value":"43-开始烧录","line":65,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-方法-b分区烧录仅更新应用":{"type":"header","text":"5. 方法 B：分区烧录（仅更新应用）","value":"5-方法-b分区烧录仅更新应用","line":71,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-烧录后如何验证":{"type":"header","text":"6. 烧录后如何验证","value":"6-烧录后如何验证","line":91,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-常见问题排查":{"type":"header","text":"7. 常见问题排查","value":"7-常见问题排查","line":98,"column":0,"depth":2},"71-工具连不上板子":{"type":"header","text":"7.1 工具连不上板子","value":"71-工具连不上板子","line":100,"column":0,"depth":3},"72-烧录成功但不启动":{"type":"header","text":"7.2 烧录成功但不启动","value":"72-烧录成功但不启动","line":107,"column":0,"depth":3},"73-启动后异常重启":{"type":"header","text":"7.3 启动后异常重启","value":"73-启动后异常重启","line":113,"column":0,"depth":3},"8-你当前这版的推荐操作":{"type":"header","text":"8. 你当前这版的推荐操作","value":"8-你当前这版的推荐操作","line":118,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"jxzspjsfkjpyzxdrn5ntdy7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bk7252n-烧录教程基于当前工程产物\">BK7252N 烧录教程（基于当前工程产物）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bk7252n-烧录教程基于当前工程产物\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"bk7252n-烧录教程基于当前工程产物-1\">BK7252N 烧录教程（基于当前工程产物）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bk7252n-烧录教程基于当前工程产物-1\"></a></h1>\n<p>本文档对应当前工程 <code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code>，并基于你刚编译得到的 <code>out</code> 目录产物。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-先确认编译产物\">1. 先确认编译产物<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-先确认编译产物\"></a></h2>\n<p>成功编译后，<code>out</code> 目录里通常有这些文件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>bootloader_bk7252n_uart1_v1.0.14.bin</code>：Bootloader</li>\n<li><code>rtthread.bin</code>：应用裸 bin</li>\n<li><code>rtthread.elf</code>：调试用 ELF</li>\n<li><code>rtthread.map</code>：链接映射</li>\n<li><code>all_4M.1220.bin</code>：整包镜像（bootloader + app）</li>\n<li><code>rtthread_uart_4M.1220.bin</code>：串口下载镜像（app 分区导出镜像）</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>推荐优先使用 <code>all_4M.1220.bin</code> 做“全量刷机”，最稳。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-烧录工具说明\">2. 烧录工具说明<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-烧录工具说明\"></a></h2>\n<p>本 SDK 自带的官方烧录器位于：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>tools/beken_program_V2.5.4/BekenProgramV2.5.4.exe</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>这是 Windows GUI 工具。<br>\n如果你现在在 Linux 环境开发，通常有三种方式：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>到一台 Windows 电脑上烧录（最常见）</li>\n<li>Linux 上用虚拟机跑 Windows 再烧录</li>\n<li>Linux + Wine 运行该 exe（兼容性不保证）</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"3-硬件连接\">3. 硬件连接<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-硬件连接\"></a></h2>\n<p>按常见 BK7252N 串口下载流程准备：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>USB 转串口连接开发板（TX/RX/GND，电平 3.3V）</li>\n<li>确认串口号（Windows 设备管理器中的 COMx）</li>\n<li>板子进入下载模式（通常是按住 Boot/Download 键上电或复位）</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>不同板卡进入下载模式的按键组合可能不同，按你主板资料为准。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-方法-a全量烧录推荐首次或异常恢复\">4. 方法 A：全量烧录（推荐，首次或异常恢复）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-方法-a全量烧录推荐首次或异常恢复\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"41-打开工具\">4.1 打开工具<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#41-打开工具\"></a></h3>\n<p>运行：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>tools/beken_program_V2.5.4/BekenProgramV2.5.4.exe</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"42-关键配置\">4.2 关键配置<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#42-关键配置\"></a></h3>\n<p>在工具中设置：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>串口：选择你的 <code>COMx</code></li>\n<li>波特率：先用默认（常见 115200；若工具推荐更高可按工具默认）</li>\n<li>下载文件：选择 <code>out/all_4M.1220.bin</code></li>\n<li>下载地址：通常工具对整包模式会自动处理；若需要手填，填 <code>0x00000000</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"43-开始烧录\">4.3 开始烧录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#43-开始烧录\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>点击下载/开始（Start/Download）</li>\n<li>若工具提示等待 Boot，请重新执行“下载模式上电/复位”</li>\n<li>看到成功日志后重启板子</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"5-方法-b分区烧录仅更新应用\">5. 方法 B：分区烧录（仅更新应用）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-方法-b分区烧录仅更新应用\"></a></h2>\n<p>适用于 Bootloader 不变、只升级应用的情况。</p>\n<p>可选文件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>out/rtthread_uart_4M.1220.bin</code>（常用于串口升级流程）</li>\n<li>或 <code>out/rtthread.bin</code>（原始 app bin）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>推荐地址（来自本次打包配置）：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>bootloader</code> 起始地址：<code>0x00000000</code></li>\n<li><code>app</code> 起始地址：<code>0x00011000</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果工具支持按地址写入：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>仅升级应用时，将 app 镜像写到 <code>0x00011000</code></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>分区烧录必须确保地址与当前分区表一致，否则会导致无法启动。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"6-烧录后如何验证\">6. 烧录后如何验证<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-烧录后如何验证\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>串口打开日志终端（115200 8N1，按工程默认）</li>\n<li>板子复位上电</li>\n<li>观察是否出现 RT-Thread 启动日志和你的应用日志</li>\n<li>执行功能自检（联网、按键、显示、音频等）</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"7-常见问题排查\">7. 常见问题排查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-常见问题排查\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"71-工具连不上板子\">7.1 工具连不上板子<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#71-工具连不上板子\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>检查 USB 转串口驱动是否正常</li>\n<li>TX/RX 是否交叉连接（PC-TX 到板-RX）</li>\n<li>GND 是否共地</li>\n<li>是否真的进入下载模式</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"72-烧录成功但不启动\">7.2 烧录成功但不启动<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#72-烧录成功但不启动\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>首次请改用“全量烧录”<code>all_4M.1220.bin</code></li>\n<li>检查是否误写了错误地址</li>\n<li>检查镜像是否对应芯片型号 <code>bk7252n</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"73-启动后异常重启\">7.3 启动后异常重启<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#73-启动后异常重启\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>查看串口启动日志定位 fault</li>\n<li>对照 <code>out/rtthread.elf</code> + <code>out/rtthread.map</code> 做地址回溯</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"8-你当前这版的推荐操作\">8. 你当前这版的推荐操作<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#8-你当前这版的推荐操作\"></a></h2>\n<p>对你当前工程，建议直接执行：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>进入下载模式</li>\n<li>用 <code>BekenProgramV2.5.4.exe</code> 选择 <code>out/all_4M.1220.bin</code></li>\n<li>地址 <code>0x00000000</code>（若工具要求）</li>\n<li>烧录完成后复位，观察串口日志</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>如果你希望，我可以继续给你补一份《Linux + Wine 运行 BekenProgram 的步骤》，以及一个“烧录前检查清单（1 分钟版）”。</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/6d428def14b8ffdc828f43\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目交接资料</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目开发记录总纲</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/b829f8956cb30987ca7cc4\">BK7252N 固件编译说明</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI ��ӡ���̼��ĵ���","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"01a79b7e7f0264a5734e0abe50acd9de","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":96},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":121},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ��������","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":143},"end":{"line":9,"column":26,"offset":166},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ��������"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"�׶��Կ����ܽ�","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":187},"end":{"line":10,"column":18,"offset":202},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"�׶��Կ����ܽ�"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":219},"end":{"line":11,"column":15,"offset":231},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tutorial"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"2026-05-01_0234-AI��ӡ���̼�������¼","alias":"������¼.2026-05-01_0234-AI��ӡ���̼�������¼","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":3,"offset":276},"end":{"line":17,"column":82,"offset":355},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"2026-05-01_0234-AI��ӡ���̼�������¼"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"2026-05-03_������ӡ��MQTT������¼","alias":"������¼.202